markets decreased 4.1, 3.2, 4.8 and 4.1 percent respectively in
the first two months of 1998.
</P>
<P>
According to SIA, sales in the two months were consistent with
the seasonal sales pattern seen in 1997 and were in line with the
industry group's forecast.
</P>
<P>
In 1997, global sales surged in the second and third quarters
after a modest first quarter.
</P>
