<HEADLINE> U.S. Broadcasters Inspect Digital Technology </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAS VEGAS, April 6 (Xinhua) -- The annual trade show for the
National Association of Broadcasters (NAB) opened here Monday with
