<HEADLINE> Computer Hacker Arrested in Canada </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, April 6 (Xinhua) -- The Royal Canadian Mounted Police
(RCMP) has arrested a 22-year-old man for allegedly breaking into
the computer systems at NASA (National Aeronautics and Space
Administration).
