<HEADLINE> Ukraine Invites Russia to Join Naval Exercise </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, April 6 (Xinhua) -- Ukraine has invited Russia's Black
Sea Fleet to join a war game, code-named Sea Breeze, from October
25 to November 4, a naval officer said Monday in Sevastopol.
</P>
<P>
The game aims to coordinate possible peacekeeping missions and
humanitarian relief efforts in a quake-stricken area, Major Andrey
Ryzhenko was quoted as saying by the Interfax-Ukraine news agency.
