said here Monday that the relations between France and China have
entered the best period in history.
</P>
<P>
Meeting with visiting Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji, Jospin said
Zhu's visit, as an important event in the bilateral relations,
will further promote the implementation of the joint declaration
signed last May by Chinese President Jiang Zemin and French
President Jacques Chirac.
</P>
<P>
