the long-term and extensive development of bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
He said that since Chirac visited China in May last year, the
relations between China and France have been developing smoothly
in the direction set by the joint declaration.
</P>
<P>
During the talks, Zhu and Jospin shared a wide range of
identical views on bilateral relations and international issues of
common concern.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese premier formally invited Jospin to visit China this
year. Jospin accepted the invitation.
</P>
<P>
Zhu will end his visit in France and back home on Tuesday. 
